            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!--End Page Title-->
    <!-- Services Section Three -->
    <section class="services-section style-two">
        <div class="auto-container">
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Text column -->
                <div class="image-column col-lg-5 col-md-5 col-sm-12" style="background-image: url(//{$smarty.server.SERVER_NAME}/assets/images/background/about-us.jpg);"><img src="//{$smarty.server.SERVER_NAME}/assets/images/background/about-us.jpg" class="w-100 d-xl-none d-lg-none d-md-none" alt="Muweleza Ritah Team cheer leader"/></div>

                <div class="text-column col-lg-7 col-md-7 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="inner-column">
                        <div class="sec-title">
                            <span class="sub-title">#inspired-by-innovations</span>
                            <h3>Who we are and what we stand for.</h3>
                            <div class="text"><strong>Our achievements have largely always been the product of steadily raising our team's levels of aspiration and expectations. </strong></div>
                        </div>
                        <p>We define ourselves as Technology for development specialists that design and implement scalable, sustainable and on demand driven scientific solutions to address simple, moderate and complex challenges in our communities.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Image Column -->
                <div class="image-column col-lg-5 col-md-5 col-sm-12" style="background-image: url(//{$smarty.server.SERVER_NAME}/assets/images/background/about-us-2.jpg);"><img src="//{$smarty.server.SERVER_NAME}/assets/images/background/about-us-2.jpg" class="w-100 d-xl-none d-lg-none d-md-none" alt="Muweleza Ritah Team cheer leader"/></div>

                <div class="text-column col-lg-7 col-md-7 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="inner-column">
                        <div class="sec-title">
                            <span class="sub-title">#What-do-we-do</span>
                            <h3>"Dreams seldom materialise on their own"</h3>
                            <div class="text"><strong>We complain not but perform to create opportunities</strong></div>
                        </div>
                        <p>Boosted Technologies is a woman led entity with focus on diversity and illusion.</p>
                        <p>The company started operations in 2021 with a team of three with objectives of <b>engaging in general business of online and offline software, systems development, programing, software and systems design and testing, maintenance, computer hardware design, development, maintenance and configurations</b>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Image Column -->


                <div class="image-column col-lg-5 col-md-5 col-sm-12" style="background-image: url(//{$smarty.server.SERVER_NAME}/assets/images/background/about-us-4.jpg);"><img src="//{$smarty.server.SERVER_NAME}/assets/images/background/about-us-4.jpg" class="w-100 d-xl-none d-lg-none d-md-none" alt="Angella and Karungi at Boosted Technologies"/></div>

                <div class="text-column col-lg-7 col-md-7 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="inner-column">
                        <div class="sec-title">
                            <span class="sub-title">#How-we-do-what-we-do</span>
                            <h3>"There is no good idea that can't be improved on"</h3>
                            <div class="text"><strong>over time, we have always held onto understanding our Vision much more better</strong></div>
                        </div>
                        <p>To have the best engineers and scientists from a market full of mediocrity and gamblers, we decided to take on the good work of training our army of tech men and women.
                        </p>
                        <p>The company recruits students interns from various universities including but not limited to <b>Makerere University, Islamic University in Uganda, Kyambogo University</b> among others and engage them in software development trainings, computer hardware designs and development trainings, business management skills among other skills which are key factor to our company growth.</p>
                        <p>it is from the student interns that we retain those who qualify and fit in our objectives. The two months we have with the interns is just sufficient to enable us decide who to join the team and who to be left go.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Image Column -->
            </div>
            <div class="services-area">
                <div class="row">
                    <!-- Feature Block Three -->
                    <div class="feature-block-three col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12" id="mission-statement">
                        <div class="inner-box">
